snippet: Egypt's President Abdel-Fattah el-Sissi met late Sunday in Saudi Arabia with one of his strongest international supporters, King Abdullah, to talk about key security issues impacting the region....

headline.print_headline: Egypt's President on First Visit to Saudi Arabia
headline.main: Egypt's President on First Visit to Saudi Arabia

lead_paragraph: Egypt's President Abdel-Fattah el-Sissi met late Sunday in Saudi Arabia with one of his strongest international supporters, King Abdullah, to talk about key security issues impacting the region.
